#TASK2  
#find the mean of the list
a=[1,5,7,6,3,4,8]
b=int(sum(a)/len(a))
print("mean of the list:",b)
#find the median of list(odd number of element)
c=int((len(a)+1)/2)
print("median of list:",c)
O/P : mean of the list: 4
      median of list: 4
      

